 R‚ÜêTEST_ANIMATE;DIR;NDAYS;I;FN;SVG;PAD;EXISTS;ROOT
‚çù Test ANIMATE generates correct SVG frame files
‚çù Uses a 3-day range, verifies file count and content
 R‚Üê1

‚çù Output directory within project
 ROOT‚Üê(‚àä‚äÉ‚éïSHELL 'pwd')~‚éïUCS 10 13
 DIR‚ÜêROOT,'/output/test_frames'
 {}‚éïSHELL 'mkdir -p ',DIR
 {}‚éïSHELL 'rm -f ',DIR,'/frame_*.svg'

‚çù Generate 3 frames: May 15-17 1974, 5h UTC, Anaheim
 (5 15 1974)(5 17 1974) 5 33.767 ¬Ø117.833 ANIMATE DIR
 NDAYS‚Üê3

‚çù Check correct number of files
 :For I :In ‚ç≥NDAYS
   PAD‚Üê'00000',‚çïI
   FN‚ÜêDIR,'/frame_',(¬Ø5‚ÜëPAD),'.svg'
   :If ~‚éïNEXISTS FN
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: missing frame file ',(¬Ø5‚ÜëPAD),'.svg'
     R‚Üê0
   :EndIf
 :EndFor

‚çù No extra frames beyond expected count
 PAD‚Üê'00000',‚çïNDAYS+1
 FN‚ÜêDIR,'/frame_',(¬Ø5‚ÜëPAD),'.svg'
 :If ‚éïNEXISTS FN
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: unexpected extra frame file found'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

‚çù Each frame must be valid fixed-height SVG
 :For I :In ‚ç≥NDAYS
   PAD‚Üê'00000',‚çïI
   FN‚ÜêDIR,'/frame_',(¬Ø5‚ÜëPAD),'.svg'
   SVG‚Üê‚äÉ‚éïNGET FN
   :If ~‚à®/'viewBox="0 0 2320 3800"'‚ç∑SVG
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: frame ',(‚çïI),' viewBox not fixed at 2320x3800'
     R‚Üê0
   :EndIf
   :If ~‚à®/'<svg '‚ç∑SVG
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: frame ',(‚çïI),' missing <svg element'
     R‚Üê0
   :EndIf
   :If ~‚à®/'</svg>'‚ç∑SVG
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: frame ',(‚çïI),' missing closing </svg>'
     R‚Üê0
   :EndIf
 :EndFor

‚çù Frames must have different dates in their titles
 SVG‚Üê‚äÉ‚éïNGET(DIR,'/frame_00001.svg')
 :If ~‚à®/'1974/5/15'‚ç∑SVG
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: frame 1 title should contain 1974/5/15'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

 SVG‚Üê‚äÉ‚éïNGET(DIR,'/frame_00003.svg')
 :If ~‚à®/'1974/5/17'‚ç∑SVG
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: frame 3 title should contain 1974/5/17'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

‚çù Clean up
 {}‚éïSHELL 'rm -rf ',DIR

 :If R
   ‚éï‚Üê'PASS: TEST_ANIMATE (3 frames verified)'
 :EndIf
